org.apache.flex.swf.tags

Class SoundStreamHeadTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.Tag
      • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.SoundStreamHeadTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITag
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SoundStreamHead2Tag

    public class SoundStreamHeadTag
extends Tag
    Represents a SoundStreamHead tag in a SWF file.

    If a timeline contains streaming sound data, there must be a SoundStreamHead or SoundStreamHead2 tag before the first sound data block . The SoundStreamHead tag defines the data format of the sound data, the recommended playback format, and the average number of samples per SoundStreamBlock.

    See Also:
    SoundStreamBlockTag
